ructural and strategic challenges these tools allow fortress to engage in and extract value from complex investments corporate mergers and acquisitions our experience in corporate mergers and acquisitions enables us to work with corporate boards of directors management and various stakeholders in order to determine optimal structuring and execution of an investment capital markets fortress has considerable capital markets expertise and has expertise in securing lowcost lowrisk financing for its investments by accessing the debt and equity capital markets includes  billion of assets from logan circle partners which closed in april  footnotes  includes  billion of aum related to comanaged funds as of q   includes  billion of aum related to the affiliated manager q  copyright   fortress investment group llc careers contact us site map terms of use privacy statement contact us  contact us  fortress investment group llc about fortress fortress overview history leadership community engagement offices our businesses alternative asset management traditional asset management principal investments public shareholders ir overview corporate governance financial reports  filings events  presentations news insights  viewpoints share information tax information investor faqs information request regulation fd policy lp login contact us home  contact us for questions about fortress its businesses and opportunities please contact us by topic below general inquiries     public company related inquiries investor and media inquiries gordon runté managing director     gruntefortresscom fortress fund investor inquiries private equity peinvestorsfortresscom credit creditinvestorsfortresscom liquid markets liquidinvestorsfortresscom investment  business opportunities opportunitiesfortresscom career opportunities for career opportunities at fortress please click here richard staropoli managing director new york richard staropoli is the managing director  global security and counterparty risk for fortress investment group llc prior to joining fortress in november  mr staropoli spent  years with the united states secret service over the course of his career he has held numerous positions within the presidential protective division the counter assault team and within the intelligence community mr staropoli has an extensive criminal investigative background in the areas of financial crimes bank fraud counterfeiting and was a us government certified polygraph examiner mr staropoli received a bs degree from the department of mechanical  aerospace engineering at new york university copyright   fortress investment group llc careers contact us site map terms of use privacy statement sediment fortress investment group  wikipedia fortress investment group from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search fortress investment group llc type public traded as nyse fig industry investment management firm private equity credit liquid markets and traditional asset management founded   years ago  headquarters  avenue of the americas new york city united states key people randal a nardone interim ceo wesley r edens cofounder principal and cochairman of the board of directors peter l briger principal and cochairman of the board of directors products investment management firm private equity credit funds railroads hedge funds and traditional asset management net income  million usd  number of employees   subsidiaries nationstar mortgage brookdale senior living former intrawest aircastle partial railamerica formerly railroad acquisition holdings newcastle investment corp reit new residential investment corp reit new senior investment group reit new media investment group website wwwfortresscom fortress investment group is an investment management firm based in new york city when fortress launched on the nyse on february   with goldman sachs and lehman brothers underwriting the ipo it was the first large private equity firm in the united states to be traded publicly as of june   the firm managed approximately  billion alternative assets in private equity liquid hedge funds and credit funds in  fortress investment group was named hedge fund manager of the year by institutional investor and management firm of the year by hfmweek fortress has previously been recognized by institutional investor as “discretionary macrofocused hedge fund of the year” for  and “creditfocused fund of the year” for both  and  contents  history  portfolio companies  controversies  response to  economic crisis  references  external links historyedit fortress investment group llc was founded as a private equity firm in  by wesley r edens a former partner at blackrock financial management inc rob kauffman businessman a managing director of ubs and randal a nardone also a managing director of ubs fortress quickly expanded into hedge funds real estaterelated investments and debt securities run by michael novogratz and pete briger both former partners at goldman sachs fortress investment groups investments grew rapidly with its private equity funds netting  between  and  as of june   fortress investment group had four core businesses totaling approximately  billion of assets under management private equity credit liquid markets and traditional asset management logan circle partners was acquired in april  in autumn  fortress hired jeff feig formerly the global head of foreign exchange at citigroup to join novogratz as cocio of the fortress macro fund however as of october   the company announced that the  billion macro fund was to close down and distribute its assets to investors this development came after feig stepped down as cocio of the fund in july  according to the firm novogratz the remaining cio was expected to retire from the firm by the end of  on february   softbank group agreed to buy fortress investment group llc for  billion portfolio companiesedit in  fortressmanaged funds acquired canadian ski resort operator intrawest north americas largest ski resort operator that also operated luxury adventure travel brands such as abercrombie  kent which was sold in august citation needed on november   railamerica inc announced that a fortressmanaged fund would acquire the company offering  per share a  premium the transaction was completed in february  fortress later sold railamerica via initial public offering in october  on may   florida east coast industries feci parent company of florida east coast railway announced that following a unanimous vote of the feci board of directors a fortressmanaged fund would acquire feci in a transaction valued at  billion the surface transportation board approved the transaction in september  although railamerica operated fec for a time the two were never merged and after the railamerica ipo fortress retained fec and still does on june   fortress announced that it would partner with centerbridge partners to acquire penn national gaming nasdaq penn an operator of casinos and horse racing venues for  billion penn national shareholders were to receive  cash for each share on july   fortress backed away from the agreement amidst the uncertain economic climate under the termination agreement penn national receives  billion consisting of a breakup fee of  million and an interestfree  billion loan from fortress centerbridge wachovia and deutsche bank fortress cochairman wesley edens assumes a seat on the board of penn national as part of the agreement fortress has taken several of its portfolio companies public such as aircastle ltd brookdale senior living inc gagfah and railamerica inc fortress has said it lost  million purchasing fraudulent promissory notes from marc dreier who had been operating a ponzi scheme fortress filed a lawsuit against the law firm dechert in an attempt to recover the loss the lawsuit was filed in new york state court alleging dechert issued a false legal opinion letter that dreier used to defraud fortress fortresss private equity investment portfolio includes aircastle limited alea group holdings bermuda ltd amresco boxclever capstead mortgage corporation cw financial services eurocastle investment limited flagler florida east coast railway gagfah gatehouse media inc global signal inc green tree servicing llc holiday retirement intrawest italfondiario kramer junction mapeley limited mbs holdings ms hub nationstar mortgage llc penn national gaming inc prime retail railamerica resg seacastle inc simon storage springleaf financial and umami burger on january   fortress investment group was the winning bidder for the assets of the montreal maine and atlantic railway a line bankrupted after the july   lacmégantic derailment of a runaway train loaded with crude oil obliterated much of historic downtown lacmégantic quebec and incinerated fortyseven of the local townfolk in march  john e giles of great lakes partners estimated a – million investment would be needed over three years to repair the line which fortress brands as the central maine and quebec railway as it is in poor condition and currently not safe for the transport of oil or dangerous goods the sale was completed on  may  for usd  million in october  it was reported by the birmingham business journal that fortress investment group had purchased the inverness corners retail center controversiesedit in  fortress acquired intrawest in a leveraged buyout three weeks before the opening of the  winter olympics in vancouver fortress failed to make payment on its loan used to buy out intrawest this caused its creditors to force intrawest to divest itself of several of its resort holdings in  and  which includes whistler blackcomb in order to reduce its debt load fortress investment group backed a german patent troll nonmanufacturing entity ipcom gmbh  co kg notorious for suing nokia for patent infringement for  billion in  many of ipcoms patents have been invalidated by the courts and millions of dollars have been incurred in legal costs fortress investment group was the primary lender to millennium development group for building the  million cad athletes village for the  winter olympics in southeast false creek vancouver british columbia financial instability in september  saw fortress investment group reportedly at the brink of bankruptcy consequently fortress was unable to provide further financing to millennium forcing the city of vancouver to pay approximately  million cad to complete the project in time for the winter olympic games the village was completed in november  the city of vancouver applied for and received legislative approval from the province of bc to borrow as much money as required to enable the project to complete fortress investment became the owner of the village after the  winter olympics response to  economic crisisedit in the wake of the economic downturn of  forbes included wesley edens and two other fortress principals among its biggest billionaire losers of  noting that edens had watched his fortune dwindle as investor redemption soared at the companys flagship fund fortress and its principals were featured in an april  vanity fair article on the adverse economic conditions facing hedge funds referencesedit  fig income statement shareholdersfortresscom retrieved  september    company profile for fortress investment group llc bloomberg retrieved  june    how private equity found power and profit in state capitols  july  – via the new york times   seymour dan february   in a first hedge fund launches on nyse associated press via washington post retrieved december     fortress investment group llc fign reuters retrieved  june    fortress investment group named institutional investor’s hedge fund manager of the year fortress investment group llc retrieved  december    company overview of fortress investment group llc businessweek retrieved  june    fortress investments shares soar after initial sale bloomberg  retrieved    citigroup fx chief jeff feig leaving bank for fortress reuters  june  retrieved  apr